## High-Level Game Design (All Features Mandatory)

### Player Fantasy

> I am the **Booker/Owner** of a multi-brand wrestling promotion called **"Ring of Champions" (ROC)**. I oversee ROC Alpha, ROC Velocity, and ROC Vanguard. An AI "Creative Director" proposes show cards for each brand and PPV/PLE event. I tweak the cards, simulate matches, track finances and contracts, handle retirements and surprise returns, manage feuds and factions, and advance the universe through in-game years — building my wrestling empire.

### Core Pillars

1. **Deep Roster Management** — 40–50+ wrestlers with rich attributes, contracts, morale, injuries, aging, and retirement.
2. **Multi-Brand Ecosystem** — 3 distinct brands with unique identities, weekly shows, and shared PPV/PLE events.
3. **Engaging Booking System** — AI-generated show cards the player refines, with meaningful match outcome decisions.
4. **Dynamic Storytelling** — Feuds, factions, surprise returns, alignment turns, and scripted Year One storylines.
5. **Realistic Business Simulation** — Attendance, revenue, expenses, sponsorships, merchandise, TV ratings, and rival promotions.
6. **Long-Term Progression** — Careers evolve over years, legends retire and return, the universe has living history.
7. **Rich Immersion** — Social media simulation, dirt sheet leaks, press conferences, locker room politics, and fan sentiment tracking.

